description: Open House Sat. 2/17 12-1:30pm. Welcome home to this luxury South Boston contemporary condo boasting high-end features throughout including an open-concept layout with high ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors, floor-to-ceiling windows offering abundant natural light, recessed lighting, elegantly appointed bathroom with Carrara marble shower. The gourmet kitchen boasts a large center island, Jenn Air stainless appliances, custom cabinetry and premium quartz countertops. Modern amenities include custom motorized blinds, large custom-fitted closets, in-unit washer/dryer, Navien tankless water heater & built-in Sonos system creating an inviting space for relaxation or entertaining. The unit also comes with a premier deeded garage parking spot with room for some extra storage. Experience sophistication and urban elegance at its best. Conveniently located a short distance to the Redline, just blocks to the beach, tons of local restaurants, shopping, and much more!
